I have had the sample of Araucaria exhibited at the Philosophical Club;
Joseph Hooker exhibited the branch at the meeting of the Philosophical Club on 24 January 1861 (Bonney (1919), pp. 135-54). & the members were delighted with it. Seemann
Berthold Seemann had been collecting in Fiji. is now on his way home with his collections: about 1000 species.
